'''詹姆斯·道格拉斯·“吉姆”·莫里森'''（{{lang-en|James Douglas "Jim" Morrison}}，{{bd|1943年|12月8日|1971年|7月3日|catIdx=M}}），是一位[[美国|美国]]创作歌手和诗人，其最出名的身份是[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]摇滚乐队[[門戶樂團|門戶樂團]]的主唱。<ref name="climate">"[http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6316743.stm ''See e.g.'', Morrison poem backs climate plea] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/6316743.stm |date=20200316013401 }}", ''[[BBC_News|BBC News]]'', January 31, 2007.</ref>莫里森早年入迷于[[弗里德里希·尼采|尼采]]、[[阿蒂尔·兰波|兰波]]和[[傑克·凱魯亞克|傑克·凱魯亞克]]的作品，并以自己的能力把它们与歌词相结合，使他成为史上最有艺术才华、最有影响力的创作歌手之一。他20岁时进入[[洛杉矶加州大学|洛杉矶加州大学]]电影学院研究生班学习，毕业后与同学[[雷·曼扎里克|雷·曼扎里克]]（Ray Manzarek）等一共4人组成[[門戶樂團|門戶樂團]]（The Doors）。莫里森因酗酒于27岁时在法国[[巴黎|巴黎]]住处的浴缸中死亡，使他成为著名的[[27俱樂部|27俱樂部]]的一员。死亡原因声称为海洛因过量，但由于没有进行尸检，真正死因至今仍有争议。<ref name="usatoday.com">{{cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-07-11-morrison-questions_N.htm |title=New questions about Jim Morrison's death |last1=Doland |first1=Angela |last2= |first2= |date=November 11, 2007 |work=Associated Press Writer Verena von Derschau in Paris contributed to this report |publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |accessdate=December 7, 2012 |archive-date=2012-06-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120622231412/http://www.usatoday.com/life/people/2007-07-11-morrison-questions_N.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>莫里森葬于巴黎[[拉雪兹公墓|拉雪兹公墓]]。

莫里森闻名于在乐队表演时即兴创作并朗诵诗歌。因他狂野的性格和舞台风格，评论家和歌迷认为他是摇滚史上最有代表性的、极富魅力和开创性的前台人(frontman)之一。<ref>Steve Huey. [http://www.allmusic.com/artist/jim-morrison-p13722/biography Jim Morrison: Biography] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/jim-morrison-p13722/biography |date=20101228185557 }}. [[Allmusic|Allmusic]].</ref> 《[[滾石雜誌|滾石雜誌]]》把他列为“史上最伟大的一百位歌手”榜单第47位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-singers-of-all-time-19691231/jim-morrison-20101202 |title=100 Greatest Singers: Jim Morrison |work=Rolling Stone |accessdate=February 1, 2013 |archive-date=2018-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180616030208/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/lists/100-greatest-singers-of-all-time-19691231/jim-morrison-20101202 |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，他在《经典摇滚》杂志“50位最伟大的摇滚歌手”中位列第22位。<ref>May 2009. ''[[Classic_Rock_(magazine)|Classic Rock Magazine]]''.</ref> 莫里森自称“高潮摇滚之王”。<ref name="DBMJ_10_30_1970">{{cite news |title=Rock Singer Sentenced |url=http://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7E4fAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ndEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=630,7400652&dq=jim+morrison&hl=en |newspaper=Daytona Beach Morning Journal |date=October 30, 1970 |page=15 |accessdate=05-07-2013 |archive-date=2019-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190430201028/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=7E4fAAAAIBAJ&sjid=ndEEAAAAIBAJ&pg=630,7400652&dq=jim+morrison&hl=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>1993年和[[門戶樂團|門戶樂團]]一起被引入[[搖滾名人堂|搖滾名人堂]]<ref>{{cite web| url =http://www.rockhall.com/inductee/the-doors| title =The Doors| publisher =滾名人堂| accessdate =2008-01-02| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080116205327/http://rockhall.com/inductee/the-doors| archivedate =2008-01-16}}</ref>。

